---
title: Steak Frites & Red Wine Gastrique with Remoulade-Style Kohlrabi Salad
description: This steak is extra special, created with the love and care you would expect in a five-star French bistro! The tender eye fillet is smothered in a red wine gastrique, lending a sweet and sour flavour to the meal. A crunchy kohlrabi salad is the perfect accompaniment, dressed in a mustard-y remoulade-style sauce for extra flavour!
